trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs" /> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs" /> que contiene los datos del evento.

trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" /> event, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" /> event, or <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" /> event of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Representa el método que controlará el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" /> o <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" /> de una clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" />.

trans-unit.source: The method specified in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventHandler> delegate is called when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging> event, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing> event, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: El método especificado en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventHandler> delegado se llama cuando un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging> eventos, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing> eventos, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting> evento se desencadena.

trans-unit.source: Page developers can provide custom handlers for Web Parts events by adding an `OnSelectedWebPartChanging` attribute, `OnWebPartClosing` attribute, or `OnWebPartDeleting` attribute to the `<asp:webpartmanager>` element in a page, and assigning a custom method name to the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Los desarrolladores de páginas pueden proporcionar controladores personalizados para los eventos de elementos Web agregando un `OnSelectedWebPartChanging` atributo, `OnWebPartClosing` atributo, o `OnWebPartDeleting` atribuir a la `<asp:webpartmanager>` elemento en una página y asignarle un nombre de método personalizado al atributo.

trans-unit.source: A custom handler can also be assigned programmatically.
trans-unit.target: También puede asignar un controlador personalizado mediante programación.

trans-unit.source: For more information on programmatically assigning an event handler, see [NIB: How to: Connect Event Handler Methods to Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/348e9600-22e3-49a2-8864-11c5bb3e98fc).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de la asignación mediante programación un controlador de eventos, vea [NIB: Cómo: conectar métodos de controlador de eventos a eventos](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/348e9600-22e3-49a2-8864-11c5bb3e98fc).
